Brook is a multifaceted character with multiple identities. Here’s a summary of the different Brook’s:

Brook is a musician and one of the main characters in the One Piece franchise. He is a skeleton who was resurrected after eating the Yomi Yomi no Mi (Revive-Revive Fruit), which allows him to return to life after death. He is a member of the Straw Hat Pirates and is known as the “Soul King”.
Brook is also the name of a professional basketball player, Brook Lopez, who plays for the Milwaukee Bucks in the National Basketball Association (NBA). He is a 7-foot-1-inch tall center and has been an NBA All-Star and a member of the NBA All-Defensive Team.
Brooke Burke is a television host and model, known for hosting several TV shows, including “Wild On!”, “Rock Star”, and “Dancing with the Stars”.
